The paper discusses a storage and memory system for data analytics, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also talks about managing data placement optimization and failure recovery, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB) and distributed systems (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the design and implementation of a single system, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper talks about managing resources and optimizing performance, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY).
